00:53:35,392 --> 00:53:38,613
but we looked at, the price was just becoming more and more prohibitive.

985
00:53:38,653 --> 00:53:43,055
That's when we decided to start rotating out those older cards and we had to do it wholesale

986
00:53:43,115 --> 00:53:46,116
because you get a television show, they print whatever.

