00:56:37,003 --> 00:56:38,743
I would sit down, I would play test it.

1035
00:56:38,783 --> 00:56:40,704
I would play test it with people that are not your friends.

1036
00:56:41,365 --> 00:56:42,685
I would play test it with strangers

1037
00:56:42,866 --> 00:56:44,266
and I would do that for at least a year.

1038
00:56:44,646 --> 00:56:47,008
And I would make changes on that with the thing with,

1039
00:56:47,488 --> 00:56:50,189
you know, we really sort of as nice

1040
00:56:50,229 --> 00:56:51,430
as you can get the cards to look.

1041
00:56:51,470 --> 00:56:53,091
I mean, that's what we did back in grad school.

1042
00:56:53,591 --> 00:56:55,972
You know, we had art, we photocopied it, cut it out.

1043
00:56:58,269 --> 00:57:00,510
these games are really, really, really hard to get right.

1044
00:57:01,251 --> 00:57:03,012
And there's a lot of group think that goes on

1045
00:57:03,332 --> 00:57:05,213
in your group of, in any group of friends.

1046
00:57:05,694 --> 00:57:09,056
And so, yeah, you know, put it out in front of people

1047
00:57:09,096 --> 00:57:10,517
that aren't your friends for about a year

